modDescription:
This mod adds a custom bike: the RAT! Similar stats to the vanilla [motorcyle](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-motorcycle/).

One seat. Unlocks with Grease Monkey 3.

## Changelog

Added new engine/horn sounds.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/bdubyah/Mods---A19/tree/master/Rat)** for A19  
**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/bdubyah/Mods---A18/tree/master/Rat)** for A18
